ch.se.inf.ethz.jcd.batman.browser.images

Class ImageResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.se.inf.ethz.jcd.batman.browser.images.ImageResource

  • public final class ImageResource
extends Object
    Class holding images used by the view. This class implements the Singleton Design Pattern. This way all images are loaded only once.
